{"tid":1612743,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"各位聲樂隊手足全面進場","createTime":"2019-10-02T10:45:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T13:17:54.000Z","uid":3261,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b70b1152ceccf7974e31e8733abfe987c893a5cb","tid":1612743,"uid":3261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T10:45:23.000Z","msg":"自6月到而家<br />\n眼見槍聲多過我哋手足既敲擊聲<br />\n嗌口號固然係一定要<br />\n但適當既敲擊聲<br />\n係可以振奮前線手足既士氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔記得大家記唔記得7月係上環信德對出發夢既時候<br />\n我哋既敲擊聲係幫到前線手足上電咁款<br />\n<br />\n所以嚟緊發夢，希望大家都可以成為聲樂隊之一<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果呢個post無用，就唔好推<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"5023ad86cf296bfc7e0796caed4d92244d75be0b","tid":1612743,"uid":3261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T10:54:01.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"41e6e15e5f2f67f4a122663d8d9092a39af70a01","tid":1612743,"uid":301592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T11:01:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"93f8a96a0fa12ed70e4898f395936f9ee4826027","tid":1612743,"uid":3261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T11:16:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"708597a4bad42fcae981ace395cd8e6a0a60539f","tid":1612743,"uid":3261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T13:17:54.000Z","msg":"推"}]}